@startuml
title Weather Station State Machine

state "Shutdown" as Shutdown
state "Running" as Running
state "Configuration" as Configuration
state "Data Collection" as DataCollection
state "Summary Preparation" as SummaryPreparation
state "Status Check" as StatusCheck
state "Controlled Mode" as ControlledMode

[*] --> Shutdown : Power Off

Shutdown --> Running : Startup/Restart

Running --> Configuration : Settings Changed or Power Saving Requested
Running --> DataCollection : Clock Triggered
Running --> SummaryPreparation : Summary Request
Running --> StatusCheck : Status Request
Running --> ControlledMode : Remote Control Command
Running --> Shutdown : Shutdown Command

Configuration --> Running : Settings Completed

DataCollection --> Running : Data Collected
SummaryPreparation --> Running : Summary Sent
StatusCheck --> Running : Status Transmitted

ControlledMode --> Shutdown : Shutdown Command
ControlledMode --> Running : Resume Command

@enduml
